'''Nova rubies''' were rare gemstones that were only known to be found on [[Sarka/Legends|Sarka]], where they were very abundant.<ref name="AE">''[[Alien Encounters]]''</ref> Nova rubies were very important to [[Galactic economy|galactic trade]], making the [[Sarkan/Legends|Sarkans]] a wealthy society.

